{"tid":1578375,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"各位手足，如果真係想幫太子同新屋嶺嘅","createTime":"2019-09-18T06:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T19:34:03.000Z","uid":274749,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"181ba06de27a16d3defec7201aec3112694ab8b0","tid":1578375,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"首先唔係文宣！！<br />\n<br />\n有心幫就做，唔好再不斷去鑽有無！好唔好？？<br />\n<br />\n有人叫我開post：<br />\n<br />\n請大概10分鐘時間做靜坐觀想，觀想天上四方八面來自宇宙的彩色光穿透建築物，照到太子站或新屋嶺入面每一個角落，照到所有亡者靈魂上，得到彩光照射之後，他們都由只有半個透明身體，逐漸回復原來的身體，身上的傷也慢慢得到自癒。（緊記：為了手足請暫時放低對popo的憎恨，觀想時儘量心懷慈悲，一心一意希望幫助亡魂，令他們的魂魄強化起來，亦令他們感覺舒暢一點。因為他們現在的狀態很辛苦。只有很多人一起這樣做，才能幫到他們。）越多人做得越密越好，救他們要快，靈體開始消失。<br />\n<br />\n再一次，唔係做文宣，你真係有心就做，唔好得個講！好唔好？！"},{"pid":"deda400e8e2984be69024f0ff05efd5c271712cc","tid":1578375,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:09:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d77ed1ef6e87fe9b02db7c4df693f40facc9e6ce","tid":1578375,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5f64dc0b2b66647e97be4c8429c9bb1f440a489d","tid":1578375,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7470178cd0c4800e5eca3645109dfd067715714e","tid":1578375,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a16b45cafbfefd147411b36eca5a950840b1d116","tid":1578375,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d5b8c2d5cfc24ce1e7656d27c4a3ed2ea328be0","tid":1578375,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ee43fb0a99be9495b66137216302574804a6877","tid":1578375,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a7db4c59d48839c08e89f1f517ea0615286c58d6","tid